title: Encens Green Tree Native Soul Copal & Palo Santo - 15 grs (French Edition)
features: Palo Santo (“Holy Wood” in Spanish) is a mystical tree that grows on the coast of South America.
Copal is a resin, once considered as sacred by Mayans and Aztecs in Mexico and Central America.
Copal and Palo Santo have been used for thousands of years by indigenous Shamans to heal the body and soul, purify spaces, clear negative energies and prepare for meditation.
These sticks wonderfully combine the sweet, piney smell of Copal with the balsamic herbal scent of Palo Santo wood, together enhancing concentration and bringing peace and harmony.
